+ * hardware DPI to a user (a settings GUI, a tray tooltip) should call
+ * this periodically.
+ *
+ * Drivers that don't implement live tracking return `-ENOTSUP`.
+ *
+ * @param device A previously initialized ratbag device
+ * @return 0 on success, a negative errno on error, `-ENOTSUP` if the
